  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>패키지 전문,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4c74a721-f3b2-4bd5-979f-fee98834817a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-397af97a-593a-49d7-aa68-c1fd6286a2c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a42ad087-8774-40f9-99f3-b3a8cca4ce6c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b394e8a9-1ea8-450d-8d7e-48c94c362033\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75214f51-a87a-4e5a-9e36-497c46f6c59b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-17aeb0b6-11c0-4255-afab-676b60b32bc0\" style=\"\">박스는 크게 3분류로 나뉩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75fb9b3d-e5a0-4438-8b21-f3c8c2b80fed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58d06979-3465-4bc4-b3a2-38e192164cc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-21bc18f6-45f8-40bd-bfab-f8bd18ff9e9d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>단상자</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4595bb6c-6757-49a6-a9ed-6d6cd0bfa1e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 종이 하나를 도무송(톰슨)작업하여 제작되는 형태를 말합니다. 거의 350g 이상의 종이로 제작이 되며 적은 비용으로 가볍게 제작이 되기 때문에  디자인이나 작업 공정도 다른 박스에 비해 효율적인 측면이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45c4045f-3633-405a-acfd-eeb9fe6d4421\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae1c5620-6375-4dbb-aa03-e8604a7639e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25489000-7e5b-46c3-a3fe-55f7ca272f3d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-995859d8-ed9a-454d-9c98-9697c86e4bca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형태로는 조립하는 형태가 있고 접착하는 형태가 있습니다. 또는 일체형이 있고 분리형도 있습니다. 기본적인 단상자의 형태는 다음 글을 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25b26575-3cec-4c18-a31c-a90cac3a045f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d358e21b-d4c2-4c07-8c5f-e8066856f36f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b45515d7-e6b3-4b27-80a4-fcc14a021b85\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a0cbe04-24d9-46ed-8e0f-3364fc3c67a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0bef7d99-32f2-423a-a2ca-a5703e6e937d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223708375876\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223708375876</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b81cdfa8-d7c9-4ffc-97c8-338b49a6426f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f41bd13-2f86-48b3-baa3-08411eb0275c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-10e0d32d-2342-4c89-8633-c6d4eef61d90\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64ca6b22-3c21-4fe9-8616-85e3fc525201\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-edd777f5-b50f-4fdf-a6f9-7967c866f626\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>골판지 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e6486032-b5a1-4d53-a751-8d9003720bfa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 보통 이야기할 때 골판지에 1도나 2도로 후렉소인쇄를 하는 경우가 많습니다. 보통 택배 박스라고도 불립니다. 또는 사과나 농수산 상자를 골판지로 두껍게 만들고 그 위에 1~2도 인쇄를 진행합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45ee39c9-3d7a-4314-be9d-b37798da3c1d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8441791f-9cc4-46c4-9a09-68b3472edb81\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18280dba-1d46-4c0a-921a-333aa10673b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7bb855df-101f-40e6-b224-75b6169189a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 인쇄물의 경우는 단위가 크고 정기적으로 발주하므로 문의하시면 친절하게 상담을 드리겠습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 조금 더 경쟁력 있는 업체를 협업을 통해 네트워크 시켜드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-27ffe500-63e1-4b1a-9f8f-41cb733c2687\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ae68850-6c0d-4a82-b7fb-bbb9be0e8e5e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ecc63c1f-d48f-4a7f-869b-22abe52592f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e768944-2dd7-427e-ab63-d207907e928c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보통은 1도나 2도 후렉소인쇄가 아닌 경우는 골판지에도 합지를 하여 진행하는 경우가 많습니다. 이런 경우를 저희는 싸바리나 합지 박스라고 부르겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3e770533-0499-4e3a-b758-34b715bd995c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-34acc9e6-69c1-4486-9f89-dd6033cb0df2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd68eb34-d500-41f5-915a-506aed9d15d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4225c7ce-59e6-4223-ae51-9d54ef60dd4a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c33964df-4246-4e12-a5bb-b8856a623676\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3951ab06-c008-4b90-9775-a6ab224e045f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>싸바리 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b83e8d9-750c-40bd-a4d9-fa9fc4c48790\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 겉지와 골지 또는 갱판지를 합지하여 튼튼하게 제작되는 박스입니다. 주로 선물 박스나 기타 여러 용도로 사용되며 단조로운 색상으로 처리하기보다 조금 더 고급스럽게 인쇄하여 튼튼한 갱판지 또는 골판지를 합하여 제작하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-290680a7-ccc7-4f79-a806-4c6601bd5355\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:688px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0e71b54d-1ff6-4956-9136-c8c90bec5b51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bca95c2b-6411-4def-96d1-c1e57ff79e10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28604d6f-a164-458d-9f9a-2304417256fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸개지와 속지를 합지하여 만들게 되며 인쇄의 홍보용과 포장재로서의 튼튼함도 갖추게 되는 박스 형태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e747d38-6445-43d0-b015-ba8e862d0cd3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ae79979-fd57-4568-9bf7-359b97aece62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95838e87-dfb3-4db0-93f2-12c576b5c0b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28f4db73-686d-47c5-8249-5b161bf58b9a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bce02ee3-27cd-456f-a3f2-84c812c21ecf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">공정이나 비용이 비싸서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a1b37197-9190-4b8c-8deb-3f13c3beb7e0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\"><b>소량 생산에는 제약</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4fdf7fd5-8c32-4e8f-9bf8-2db3106c0577\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">이 있습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 소량 샘플 제작을 준비하고 있습니다. 가장 합리적인 방법으로 샘플 싸바리를 만들 수 있도록 노력하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2511fe27-ebbf-4adf-a1d1-74ad5382e125\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-caffaec2-5f5b-46c8-a52e-ba6582ddfd51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe2d4316-8fed-4276-92af-a3f7b8c8d461\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-66dea968-89d3-47f9-9f3b-9fa9bfd7d6e4\" style=\"\">여러분은 어떤 박스를 선택하실까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c519850-1e78-454c-beed-1f2701d0b849\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6cde12c9-45f6-4775-a3a6-d4cdef9067c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05a6c01d-ca8e-4093-8dc3-fde39ab4e6bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님께서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bb8963bd-7187-4c90-bf29-3701cc1808c1\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>화장품</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dd7ae8fc-2b39-4343-a0fd-7c34e57c03b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 제작하는 회사의 대표시라면 여러 가지 박스를 주문하실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d72645c2-175a-47df-90e2-6047522169c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-26ce5249-a562-4068-8813-53e84e55ec67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-475f6862-c358-4508-9ece-3535319b8a50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86693a07-1161-400f-8947-68b85a70daa6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하나의 제품을 편하게 쇼핑몰로 판매하는 상품이라면 화장품 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-08ce8055-2e01-4b8b-8eec-b9f0dd851c92\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단상자</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1925d374-f35b-4883-9ddd-4103faa61e50\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 생산할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f69b6c24-a753-46db-856e-b008f289ff14\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53d42b02-7c63-4011-834e-5d199acdb3e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76372e60-c4f3-4391-893d-64a08c76cc2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-423fa3d8-8e5d-4a9a-bdef-b3b543a53ac0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23092c25-50aa-41df-888b-0533106f60a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eee20651-2e7b-4968-93c3-4ad8a0251962\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 세트로 만들어서 더 튼튼한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91228bd6-7f95-44ba-b468-3227d4618812\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸바리박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ce71b0d-7aaa-4ea2-a131-6141e3ac83a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-41e401d4-91aa-452d-8602-91e4ecf02a62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b112901-5f52-4e78-aada-e9cf393a3db9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-728cb77f-682f-42f7-866d-cd934d1876b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f158581-ff25-4475-ad83-dfb493205e04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b9ae5ead-5a77-429b-b03b-01492742bc83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7b5cc64-8668-4b65-a17f-d481b4209f4c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11f86b4e-c811-4727-8503-cbfee6236a93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d707458e-2032-48b6-9cc0-114c639230a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또 이런 박스들을 모두 모아 한 번에 패킹하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a12c2c52-b6f2-46e8-95a7-9dee80ea809c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>카톤 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc682595-6110-4c91-a011-a18677129bcc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3c37498b-817d-4c92-8685-1d889310fe5f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223794795867/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dde7fdb2-34ee-4cc8-a4f3-d5b40e6ef4d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40c904cf-4429-40c4-8179-7e5f5e7b85a7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b14ba67c-0e5e-4d26-b38f-d21fbb69d6ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이처럼 제품의 성격과 무게 또는 받는 사람에 따라 분류하여 자신에게 가장 잘 맞는 상자의 형태나 종류를 선택하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8e3b60f-f89d-44de-8b76-6b1e28f38d91\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f48e769-c18b-4af1-adcd-09472e340d80\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47c5fe2d-07d1-473f-95e2-8526f8849df4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99cc1f8e-62d9-4329-9afd-575900cc93c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 요청하시면 방문이나 전화상담을 통해 친절하게 협의나 조언 드리도록 하겠습니다. 언제나 고객과 함께하는 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223794795867#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
